dct_title_s: Map of Minneapolis, Hennepin Co., Minn., 1895. Plate 3 b, Paving
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:24,000]. 2,000 ft. to 1 in. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Shows pavement material of streets, street car lines and railroads, and parks. "Plate 3 b.--Paving." Dimensions: 72 x 47 centimeters
